**VertCoin** (VTC) was created in early 2014 to overcome concerns that the centralization of mining that has occurred with Bitcoin, has reduced the security of Bitcoin. (1.1)  VertCoin is advertised as being [[ASIC|Mining#ASIC_Mining]] resistent and [[multipool]] resistant. (1.2) 

